{"tid":1715673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大學生：警察昨進攻中大像為宣示主權 不能讓他們得逞","createTime":"2019-11-13T06:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T07:50:43.000Z","uid":212626,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"35507dd58fdd85ecaaa567cad1541532584493cc","tid":1715673,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:54:33.000Z","msg":"中大二號橋有過百人留守，當中包括中大學生以及其他院校的學生。<br />\n<br />\n有中大學生說，不想校園被警察攻陷，守護校園的象徵意義大，警察濫權不能無止境。<span style=\"color: red;\">他認為，警察昨日進攻中大好像為宣示主權，不能讓他們得逞</span>。<br />\n<br />\n有來自其他大學的學生說，若警察成功入侵中大，即大學校園失守，因此今早特別前來支援，又說所屬的大學有警察進入，也需要其他學生來幫忙守護。亦有學生認為，中大校方應對學生與警方對峙的場面，反應太遲，管理層應及早站出來交涉。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491866-20191113.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491866-20191113.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaSPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=ad765f0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491866-20191113.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7c17073e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491866-20191113.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c72b14072c093776c04c52f458db42a11cf04b30","tid":1715673,"uid":309045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:55:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11f19c75e8f395f6b6e1779c983a998d283977f","tid":1715673,"uid":263648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35507dd58fdd85ecaaa567cad1541532584493cc","tid":1715673,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:54:33.000Z","msg":"中大二號橋有過百人留守，當中包括中大學生以及其他院校的學生。<br />\n<br />\n有中大學生說，不想校園被警察攻陷，守護校園的象徵意義大，警察濫權不能無止境。<span style=\"color: red;\">他認為，警察昨日進攻中大好像為宣示主權，不能讓他們得逞</span>